still trying to verify the report 
the united church of christ has been widely criticized by the 
military for alleged links with communist rebels because of the 
denominations outspoken stand on human rights 
in the past most beheadings in mindanao have been carried out by 
religious fanatics who are frequently used by the military to fight 
the communists 
