possible time for an oil spill said kenneth sherman of the national 
marine fisheries service fish can swim away from the slick but 
larvae dont have that mobility he said 
diprete said the captain of the greeklicensed world prodigy 
iakovis georgudis admitted he failed to wait for a pilot and 
mistakenly changed course sending the ship toward rocks 
hours after the accident a tanker and an oil barge collided in 
the houston ship channel that connects the texas city with galveston 
bay causing a spill and early saturday heavy oil spilled in the 
delaware river after an uruguayan tanker ran aground 
results of drug tests on georgudis and a mate whose name was not 
immediately available were expected by late today although the 
