electronics and other assembly lines have partially shut down 
hospitals and pharmacies are short on medical supplies and la 
serenisima one of the largest dairies has filed for bankruptcy 
no payments have been made on the foreign debt since last year 
and argentina is about 4 billion in arrears the central bank has 
only about 140 million in foreign reserves menem said and new 
loans from abroad are unlikely 
the budget deficit and unemployment are growing real wages have 
shrunk by at least 30 percent so far this year 
menem describes the argentina he will inherit as poisoned 
calamitous and chaotic and says he has fashioned a government of 
national unity to improve it 
those who criticized me most severely in the past now 
understand that they were wrong he said monday 
i hope my supporters who are now raising their voices finally 
