<TEXT>
the idea was planted 11 years ago by a public 
school teacher in the south bronx find gifted minority students 
give them some intensive instruction and place them in exclusive 
private schools 
this spring that idea bore fruit 
some of the finest universities in the country princeton 
northwestern pennsylvania oberlin gave degrees to 10 students 
