elderly americans are hospitalized each year by adverse drug 
reactions we suspect the number is considerably larger because 
many hospitalizations are wrongly blamed on patients diseases 
rather than their medicines he said 
the republic estimated 19 million such hospitalizations yearly 
the pharmaceutical manufacturers association lacks data on 
